{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "\u00a31 tax on top division football league tickets to fund community 3G pitches",
        "additional_details": "I believe a \u00a31 tax is very little and could be affordable for top league teams to contribute towards. This could help protect grassroots football and help develop our players further in the cold wet winter months, which other countries don\u2019t have to face. Matches could still be able to go ahead and enable our next generation of top British players to continue to develop.",
        "background": "Currently, many football games are getting postponed due to the weather affecting grass pitches. I call on the Government to impose a \u00a31 tax on every top division football league ticket to fund community 3G pitches for grassroots teams in bad weather conditions via a \u201cLet The Kids Play fund.\u201d",
